{"author": "Joel Osteen", "text": "You must make a decision that you are going to move on. It wont happen automatically. You will have to rise up and say, \u2018I don\u2019t care how hard this is, I don\u2019t care how disappointed I am, I\u2019m not going to let this get the best of me. I\u2019m moving on with my life.", "tags": ["disappointment", "failure", "moving-on"]}
{"author": "William Shakespeare", "text": "Words are easy, like the wind; Faithful friends are hard to find.", "tags": ["friendship"]}
