{"author": "Charles Bukowski", "text": "Find what you love and let it kill you.", "tags": ["love"]}
{"author": "Philip K. Dick", "text": "Reality is that which, when you stop believing in it, doesn't go away.", "tags": ["belief", "real-life", "reality"]}
